##Huaxing optronics response to "forced Rework" storm: Will Not directly fire employees, strengthen the protection of the plant

Resumption of normal production may face the risk of an epidemic, the shutdown would mean huge losses.

”

Recently, due to the forced return of Wuhan employees to work, Wuhan Huaxing Optoelectronics Technology Co. , Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as "Huaxing Optoelectronics") was pushed to the top of the storm.

According to the report, in order to quickly replace the first-line Staff, Wuhan Huaxing Optoelectronics some departments have begun to take "compulsory" rework measures, no longer to work according to absenteeism treatment, more than a certain period of time automatically quit.

A person close to huaxing optoelectronics in Wuhan told interface news that since February 14, some departments of Huaxing optoelectronics have started to inform employees by phone to return to Wuhan for work. Failure to return may lead to dismissal. This has raised concerns among many employees. As of 11:00 a.m. on Feb. 21,319 new cases had been confirmed in Wuhan, the city at the center of the outbreak, bringing the total to 45,346.

In response to the storm, the parent company of Huaxing Optoelectronics, TCL  , told interface news that employees who are temporarily unable to return to work will not be dismissed directly, and attendance will be handled in accordance with the relevant policies of the Hubei Provincial Bureau of Human Resources and social welfare. At the same time, Huaxing has also opened offices in Shenzhen, South Korea, Taiwan, Beijing and other places. Under the premise of safeguarding the health of employees, Huaxing has tried its best to ensure that the company is in good operation.

As China's panel industry hub, Wuhan has gathered Beijing East, Huaxing Optoelectronics, Shentianma three big head enterprise five production lines.

After the outbreak of new crown pneumonia, at the center of the storm Huaxing photoelectric left-behind staff under tremendous pressure. According to the convention, Huaxing optronics staff will stay at the factory during the Spring Festival every year to ensure the normal operation of the machines. But this year affected by the epidemic, left-behind employees have been working overtime for many days.

"At least 20 days have been worked since January 22,2009, and the physical and psychological limits have been reached, " said a huaxing employee, under normal circumstances, colleagues on duty during the Spring Festival to the sixth day can take leave, but now years ago colleagues can not return to Wuhan to replace.

"The contradiction now is that if we stop the work completely, the enterprise will lose a lot. But if we don't stop the work, the safety of the employees will be at risk, " the employee said, a modest cut in output is a compromise, and even a half cut in February would have little impact on overall corporate profits.

On Feb. 12, TCL's chairman, Li Dongsheng, said in a Weibo Post that due to the special process of semiconductor display industry, continuous production is required and employees work every day. Under the pressure of the epidemic, TCL Huaxing people in Shenzhen and Wuhan remained on duty to ensure the normal operation of the factories, especially the Wuhan Huaxing Factory, with 7,000 employees under the leadership of the core management.

"because Wuhan Huaxing low-temperature polysilicon screens account for 20 per cent of the global supply, the shutdown has had an impact on the global industrial chain. And with the city sealed off, the risk of leaving the site could be even greater. We are working and living in strict accordance with the requirements of prevention and control, while keeping the plant running normally, there is no outbreak in the plant area,"Li Dongsheng said.

Internal staff also confirmed that the panel factory once the shutdown will cause significant losses to the enterprise.

What's special about chips and panels is that there's a lot of circuitry stacked in a small space, so the circuitry needs to be a three-dimensional design of layer after layer, with each layer perfectly aligned to the next. If the production line is stopped, then some of them may have made two layers, some of them made four or five layers, seven or eight layers. When the production line is opened again, the machine stand idle will cause loss of accuracy and damage to its life, even if the deviation is a few percent, the production is also a waste product, the loss is huge, and the cost of re-construction is huge.

The Wuhan plant is vital to Huaxing optronics.

On February 11, TCL said publicly that the Wuhan Huaxing T3 panel production line continued to be full production, and in January completed ahead of schedule, the current production capacity of 50K / month, materials and manpower can meet the current production needs, finished goods shipping channel normal. From February 1 to February 10,2020, the cumulative T3 casting volume was the same as the same period last year, is expected to continue full production operations in February.

According to the reporters, Huaxing Photoelectric Wuhan area of the production line to a small size, Wuhan's panel revenue accounted for about 40% of the group's revenue last year. An internal senior worry, if the Wuhan plant staff still can not come back in the next two weeks, the latter module will have some orders can not be delivered.

In the call for staff to return to work colleagues, Huaxing optoelectronics still need to prevent the epidemic. As of 20:00 on February 15,263 people had been found to have fever, cough and other abnormal conditions at Huaxing, Wuhan, according to an internal report by Huaxing optronics that has been circulated. All of them have been sent to medical treatment, 218 of whom have been ruled out by hospital diagnosis, the dormitory on the factory campus quarantined 45 people by itself, among which 25 people were quarantined by the close or indirect contact fever people.

In this regard, Huaxing Guangdian explained that: Before the relevant media articles attached to the notice for the company's Daily public to all employees to push the epidemic prevention and control notice. They involved the confirmed case of infection during the staff leave, the second day found that day isolation, contact with 20 people were also immediately isolated observation. The related quarantined personnel daily health test, and nucleic acid test are negative, no abnormality, confirmed that the staff is now good physical recovery.

Huaxing photoelectric side clearly said that at present, Wuhan Huaxing no cases of infection caused by the emergence within the company.

In addition, Wuhan Huaxing is also continuing to strengthen the epidemic prevention measures, will carry out dormitory area / Office area / shuttle bus / public facilities comprehensive disinfection (2 times / Day) ; At the same time, it will meet the living needs and health requirements of the left-behind employees in the aspects of board and lodging.
